{"arkId":"cl010259207","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010259207","modified ":"2025-11-22","title":"l\u00e9cythe","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"D\u00e9nomination","value":"l\u00e9cythe"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : archa\u00efque ; figures noires\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 3e quart VIe s. av. J.-C. (vers -540)","currentLocation":"non expos\u00e9","room":"","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":-540,"endYear":"","imprecision":"vers","text":"3e quart VIe s. av. J.-C.","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[],"objectNumber":[{"value":"CA 1340","type":"Num\u00e9ro d\u0027entr\u00e9e"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Antiquit\u00e9s grecques, \u00e9trusques et romaines","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"D\u00e9cor : sur col (en bas) ; filet ; motif en Z (file) ; sur \u00e9paule ; fleur et bouton de lotus (frise) \r\nsur panse (devant) ; H\u00e9rakl\u00e8s et le lion de N\u00e9m\u00e9e ; H\u00e9rakl\u00e8s (cheveux, court, bandeau, imberbe, chit\u00f4n, court, brod\u00e9, draperie, baudrier, massue, attaquant) ; lion (rugissant) ; dans le champ ; tache (4)\r\n\r\nEtat de l\u0027oeuvre : le vase est entier ; des petits \u00e9clats ; des nombreuses concr\u00e9tions ;le vernis est \u00e9caill\u00e9 par endroits ; il est possible que certaines incisions ont \u00e9t\u00e9 refaites.","inscriptions":"Inscription : \r ; peinte dans le champ entre H\u00e9racl\u00e8s et le lion\r ; Langue : \r ; grecque\r ; Nature du texte : \r ; acclamation (contenu du texte-\u003Eformule diverse)\r ; moderne (?)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"14,4","displayDimension":"14,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"8,9","displayDimension":"8,9 cm","unit"